### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = <pega_tu_token_aqui>
@extraProductId = <pega_el_id_del_extra>
@productCategoryId = <pega_el_id_de_la_categoria>

### ─────────────────────────────
### EXTRA PRODUCTS
### ─────────────────────────────

### Crear producto (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/extra-products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Fanta",
  "category_id": "{{productCategoryId}}",
  "price": 1200
}

###

### Crear otro producto (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/extra-products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Ensalada César",
  "category_id": "{{productCategoryId}}",
  "price": 3500
}

###

### Listar todos los extras
GET {{baseUrl}}/extra-products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar productos extra paginados
GET {{baseUrl}}/extra-products?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener extra por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/extra-products/one?extraProductId={{extraProductId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Actualizar extra (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/extra-products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{extraProductId}}",
  "name": "Ensalada César Actualizada",
  "category_id": "{{productCategoryId}}",
  "price": 3800,
  "active": true
}

###

### Desactivar extra (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/extra-products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{extraProductId}}",
  "name": "Ensalada César",
  "category_id": "{{productCategoryId}}",
  "price": 3500,
  "active": false
}

###

### Eliminar extra (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/extra-products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{extraProductId}}"
}

###
